Dear Sir/Madam,

I am writing on behalf of the residents of [Name of area/colony], [City], to bring to your attention the inadequate and irregular water supply in our area. We have been facing this issue for the past [duration] and it has reached a critical level.

The water supply in our area has been inconsistent and unpredictable, making it difficult for us to carry out our daily activities. It has become a norm for us to go without water for days on end, forcing us to rely on alternate sources such as water tankers, which are not only expensive but also unreliable. This has caused a significant financial burden on the residents, especially the low-income households.

Moreover, the water that is supplied to our area is often contaminated and unfit for consumption. We have noticed a foul smell and discoloration in the water, but despite repeated complaints to the local authorities, no action has been taken to address this issue. This has put the health of our community at risk.

